references: Repealing: Ord 3342, Ord 5480, Ord 5692, Ord 6219, Ord 6577, Ord 7198, Ord 7417, Ord 7431, Ord 7451, Ord 8341, Ord 8639, Ord 9036
summary: An Ordinance regulating the construction of sidewalks, in the City of Seattle, and repealing Ordinances Nos. 3342, 5480, 5692, 6219, 6577, 7198, 7417, 7431, 7451, 8341, 8639, 9036, relating to the construction of sidewalks, and all other ordinances or parts of ordinances in conflict herewith, and providing a penalty for the violation hereof.
